{"tid":1458471,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[向大陸電Say no] 「長遠減碳策略」公眾諮詢","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T18:30:25.000Z","uid":267806,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"300241798d9f2d9cc9ee655bccc89ff01e1eb308","tid":1458471,"uid":267806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"可能依家風頭火勢大家冇左件事<br />\n但係我要提提大家記得去報名參加公眾諮詢會啊！！！<br />\n就係<span style=\"color: red;\">今個星期三同四</span>就舉行架啦！！<br />\n快d報名啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.susdev.org.hk/tc/register.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.susdev.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fregister.php&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWle2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=d3c5d585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.susdev.org.hk/tc/register.php</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有千其唔好唔記得公眾諮詢期deadline係9月20號<br />\n即係9月20號之前要表明反對向大陸買電啊！<br />\n填form唔夠架，最好要send埋一份有理有據的意見書，仲要要求回覆先有最大效果。<br />\n個向大陸買電計劃你可以禁上面條link耐心d睇<br />\n個仆街政府係搵埋歐盟國家有renewable energy既互相聯網為理據，要香港效發佢地向大陸買更多核電！<br />\n注意，係更多，唔好同我講大亞灣已經係乜乜77<br />\n目前小妹大約諗左幾個point，希望可以拋鏄引玉，可以諗到更多更好同完善好呢d論點<br />\n<br />\n1. 核電比碳排放影響更深遠，以環保角度而言，不應單單為減碳而增加本就受爭議的核電比例，否則只係為跑數而跑數，而非真正為環保<br />\n<br />\n2. 現在中電同港燈都計劃增加天然氣比例，不但正在興建新的燃氣發電機組，堆填區焚化爐（定燒堆填區廢氣唔記得左，仲有計劃興建嘅液化天然氣接收站，太陽能Feed-in Tariff鼓勵發展太陽能等等，買大陸電完全係多此一舉<br />\n<br />\n3. 眾所周知香港的供電穩定性係全球首屈一指，兩間香港電力公司的穩定度至少皆有99.999℅（希望冇錯），而中國南方電網的穩定度遠遠低於香港（實際數字唔記得）。 難道為左環保，我地就要犧牲更多停電的風險嗎？香港停一次電的經濟損失可以數以千萬計，你擔當得起嗎？<br />\n<br />\n4. Paris Agreement畢竟冇legal binding force，點解要將個deadline set到咁快呢？<br />\n<br />\n大家記得唔好跟政府提供嘅思路誤導，要問出香港市民關心嘅，就要自己dup意見書<br />\n<br />\n而最最最緊急嘅係，記得報名參加公眾討論會啊！！！<br />\n強烈建議禁返我上面po條link睇哂個proposal寫左咩，然後對症下藥準備論據質詢。<br />\n<br />\n和理非們，做野啦！！！"},{"pid":"f57d9bd5f480b069e753c246a9ef7cbe91bcb58a","tid":1458471,"uid":267806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a9c6e7226d8384adafa70c9ff0bde1ec6ffb21","tid":1458471,"uid":267806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:08:12.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecffa6b960851bcd58381eb72d7243913d7ebcae","tid":1458471,"uid":108360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:09:59.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"22d6bf47bff2264e6870a91fdcbf55d557573072","tid":1458471,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:12:38.000Z","msg":"岩岩聽到大陸親戚汕尾市又停電<br />\n佢地話成日都會<br />\n<br />\n香港係咪要不時都停一停電"},{"pid":"39a69b72c89b8118830cf5814e1a13fa9ed9f0c6","tid":1458471,"uid":267806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"22d6bf47bff2264e6870a91fdcbf55d557573072","tid":1458471,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:12:38.000Z","msg":"岩岩聽到大陸親戚汕尾市又停電<br />\n佢地話成日都會<br />\n<br />\n香港係咪要不時都停一停電"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"歡迎巴打可以再搵多d呢d case幫手整彈藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90405128b57f7ab71b6d6e24abb5c7b8fc212f3e","tid":1458471,"uid":267806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:21:23.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9c1f9fb7243b219f86e25eec16fa272330e32d","tid":1458471,"uid":172081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"10751c8f2bf1709836144502d945cceb870dfdfc","tid":1458471,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\